      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, so we're in I. O. S. And we reach renters in a number of different ways. Just rolled out a product and wanted to see if any properties that you have might be struggling or could use a boost uh an occupancy and and see how we could could step in and help out in any of those properties."
