      "recording_attendee_id": "1c2cfd22-6e49-4c4f-8748-59f2e2a13f6d",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "You know, surprisingly we're doing pretty well now. I mean everything's running so we don't we don't really have any problems with that right now. We've had some in the past but not now."
