      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "Yeah. Okay. Okay. Makes sense because I was on your website earlier and and saw a handful of I think single family homes um that were available and we work in that space as well. So uh just wanted to see if you could use a push offering month to month contract, so not locking in anything long term. Um But if"
